trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection class represents a set of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CmsRecipientCollection representerer et sett med <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: CmsRecipientCollection implements the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.
trans-unit.target: CmsRecipientCollection implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsRecipientCollection oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> class and adds the specified recipient.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsRecipientCollection oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> klasse og legger til den angitte mottakeren.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> class that represents the specified CMS/PKCS #7 recipient.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> klasse som representerer den angitte mottakeren CMS/PKCS #7.

trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> class and adds recipients based on the specified subject identifier and set of certificates that identify the recipients.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsRecipientCollection oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> klasse og legger til mottakere som er basert på angitte emne-IDen og sett med sertifikater som identifiserer mottakerne.

trans-unit.source: A member of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"></xref> enumeration that specifies the type of subject identifier.
trans-unit.target: Et medlem av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"> </xref> opplisting som angir hvilken type emne identifikator.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"></xref> collection that contains the certificates that identify the recipients.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"> </xref> samlingen som inneholder sertifikater som identifiserer mottakerne.

trans-unit.source: The Add method adds a recipient to the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Add-metode legger til en mottaker til den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object that represents the recipient to add to the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objektet som representerer mottakeren for å legge til den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: If the method succeeds, the method returns an <xref:System.Int32> value that represents the zero-based position where the recipient is to be inserted.
trans-unit.target: Hvis metoden lykkes, returneres en <xref:System.Int32>verdi som representerer den nullbaserte plasseringen der mottakeren skal settes inn.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: If the method fails, it throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis metoden mislykkes, oppstår det et unntak.

trans-unit.target: recipientis .

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method copies the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection to an array.
trans-unit.target: CopyTo metoden kopier av <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling til en matrise.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Array> object to which the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection is to be copied.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Array>objektet som den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samlingen er som skal kopieres.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` where the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection is copied.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen i `array` der den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samlingen kopieres.

trans-unit.source: - array is not large enough to hold the specified elements.
trans-unit.target: - arrayer ikke stort nok til de angitte elementene.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method copies the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection to a <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> array.
trans-unit.target: CopyTo metoden kopier av <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling til en <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> matrise.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> objects where the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection is to be copied.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objekter der den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samlingen er som skal kopieres.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index for the array of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> objects in `array` to which the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection is copied.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen for en rekke <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objekter i `array` som den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samlingen kopieres.

trans-unit.source: - array is not large enough to hold the specified elements.

trans-unit.target: -- eller - - array inneholder ikke riktig antall dimensjoner.

trans-unit.source: The Count property retrieves the number of items in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Count-egenskapen henter antall elementer i den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> value that represents the number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int32>verdi som Representer antall elementer i samlingen.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: The GetEnumerator method returns a <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator"></xref> object for the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEnumerator returnerer en <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator"> </xref> objekt den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator"></xref> object that can be used to enumerate the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator"> </xref> objekt som kan brukes til å liste opp de <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: The IsSynchronized property retrieves whether access to the collection is synchronized, or thread safe.
trans-unit.target: IsSynchronized egenskapen henter om tilgang til samlingen er synkronisert, eller tråd trygt.

trans-unit.source: This property always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, which means that the collection is not thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>, som betyr at samlingen ikke er trygt tråd.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> value of <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, which means that the collection is not thread safe.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Boolean>verdien <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>, som betyr at samlingen ikke er trygt tråd.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: The Item property retrieves the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Elementet egenskapen henter den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objektet i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> value that represents the index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int32>verdi som Representer indeks i samlingen.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: The index is zero based.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen er nullbasert.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objektet i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: The value of an argument was outside the allowable range of values as defined by the called method.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for et argument var utenfor det tillatte verdiområdet som er definert av metoden kall.

trans-unit.target: Remove-metoden fjerner en mottaker fra den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object that represents the recipient to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objektet som representerer mottaker som skal fjernes fra samlingen.

trans-unit.target: SyncRoot egenskapen henter en <xref:System.Object>objektet brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samlingen.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> object that is used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>objekt som brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samlingen.</xref:System.Object>
